MocroProject2

Project Description
MocroProject2 is a web application that implements a fixed navbar, a floating help icon, and sticky social share icons. 

Features
- Fixed Navbar:** The navigation bar stays at the top of the page as the user scrolls.
- Floating Help Icon: A help icon that is always visible at the bottom right corner of the page.
- Sticky Social Share Icons: Social icons that attach to the navbar when the user scrolls past a certain point.
- Text Area: A read-only text area displaying default text from the Figma design.